title: WhamBam Mother Bhumi Food Stall
typeOfFood: Vegan, Indian, Fast food, Take-out only
description: A mobile snack van that serves vegan and gluten-free pakoras and bhajias freshly cooked while you wait. Uses locally grown vegetables. Takes bookings for events including local fairs, regional festivals and private parties. Operates within a 60 mile radius of Tunbridge Wells and Brighton. See website for locations and hours.
